<h4 id="経費けいひと自腹じばら">経費(けいひ)と自腹(じばら)</h4>
<ol>
  <li>このおもちゃ、経費で買ってくれる？(buy me this cat using company expense account)</li>
  <li>自腹でお願いします: pay for it out of your own pocket</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="1-名前">1. 名前</h4>
<ol>
  <li>健(ken), 譲(Joe)</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="2-福袋とお得とくと損">2. 福袋とお得(とく)と損</h4>
<ol>
  <li>僕が入っていたら超お得じゃない？If I were in your “lucky bag”, wouldn’t be a great deal.
    <ul>
      <li>In Japan many stores and restaurants are closed on January 1st,</li>
      <li>the stores stuff various random contents in a bag and sell them as 福袋 on January 1st.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>得: gain
    <ul>
      <li>お得な商品: good bargain, special account</li>
      <li>お得情報: information for good deals</li>
      <li>美女は得だよね: pretty girls get advantage</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>損: loss</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="2-稽古けいこと練習">2. 稽古(けいこ)と練習</h4>
<ol>
  <li>お節料理: special New year’s food prepared in square boxes.</li>
</ol>
